  "detailed_description": "Solar Storm is a turn-based Scifi Artillery game with lots of <strong>Explosions and Unique Weapons</strong>.<br><br>Play casually with your friends in <strong>Procedural </strong>and <strong>fully Destructible Arenas</strong> to see who is the best! Supports up to 32 players. Ideal as a party game!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/8124ca27aa380e3bff42dec1fe169746.avif?t=1727516037\" width=580 height=120 /></span><br>There are tons of <strong>Weapons, Powerups and Weapon Modes</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/bee0be73907c575c8709f3c5bd3ee496.poster.avif?t=1727516037\" width=600 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/bee0be73907c575c8709f3c5bd3ee496.webm?t=1727516037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/bee0be73907c575c8709f3c5bd3ee496.mp4?t=1727516037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/9a00e4586efb10cfd6cfd4aad7b77620.poster.avif?t=1727516037\" width=600 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/9a00e4586efb10cfd6cfd4aad7b77620.webm?t=1727516037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/9a00e4586efb10cfd6cfd4aad7b77620.mp4?t=1727516037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bounce!</h2>With <i>Bounce Projectiles</i> you can get some incredible trick shots!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/a29fc4366c62cd0eccbea6a78bdb48dd.poster.avif?t=1727516037\" width=600 height=386 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/a29fc4366c62cd0eccbea6a78bdb48dd.webm?t=1727516037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/a29fc4366c62cd0eccbea6a78bdb48dd.mp4?t=1727516037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Drill!</h2>Oh, you're stuck under the ground? The enemy is behind a wall? Sounds like you need a <strong><i>Drill Projectile</i></strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/bcae91da715f13c144cbe7fa8c94b0bb.poster.avif?t=1727516037\" width=600 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/bcae91da715f13c144cbe7fa8c94b0bb.webm?t=1727516037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/bcae91da715f13c144cbe7fa8c94b0bb.mp4?t=1727516037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/d7bdf050a112d0beb1fd08559eedefc9.avif?t=1727516037\" width=500 height=120 /></span> <br><strong>The Battles take place in fully destructible and random maps.</strong><br><br>Each has unique properties, some might be very windy and have fast-rising water, while others commonly have Earthquakes and Meteorite Storms.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/772925252c689191b7b4d669386f2b6e.poster.avif?t=1727516037\" width=600 height=321 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/772925252c689191b7b4d669386f2b6e.webm?t=1727516037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fully Destructible Terrain!</h2>Many weapons can cause explosions that destroy parts of the terrain. With a good aim, you can eliminate an enemy by strategically destroying the ground under them, sending them to the water below!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/ad9ad33c77c0a5297fe8b0290a6cb39e.avif?t=1727516037\" width=530 height=120 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Disasters can be surprisingly deadly!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/2168b0a3a0dfe44c3c7b9cf97688e87f.poster.avif?t=1727516037\" width=600 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/2168b0a3a0dfe44c3c7b9cf97688e87f.webm?t=1727516037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/2168b0a3a0dfe44c3c7b9cf97688e87f.mp4?t=1727516037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Solar Storm is a turn-based Scifi Artillery game with lots of <strong>Explosions and Unique Weapons</strong>.<br><br>Play casually with your friends in <strong>Procedural </strong>and <strong>fully Destructible Arenas</strong> to see who is the best! Supports up to 32 players. Ideal as a party game!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/8124ca27aa380e3bff42dec1fe169746.avif?t=1727516037\" width=580 height=120 /></span><br>There are tons of <strong>Weapons, Powerups and Weapon Modes</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/bee0be73907c575c8709f3c5bd3ee496.poster.avif?t=1727516037\" width=600 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/bee0be73907c575c8709f3c5bd3ee496.webm?t=1727516037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/bee0be73907c575c8709f3c5bd3ee496.mp4?t=1727516037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/9a00e4586efb10cfd6cfd4aad7b77620.poster.avif?t=1727516037\" width=600 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/9a00e4586efb10cfd6cfd4aad7b77620.webm?t=1727516037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/9a00e4586efb10cfd6cfd4aad7b77620.mp4?t=1727516037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bounce!</h2>With <i>Bounce Projectiles</i> you can get some incredible trick shots!<br><span class=\"bb_i