mstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/772925252c689191b7b4d669386f2b6e.poster.avif?t=1727516037\" width=600 height=321 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/772925252c689191b7b4d669386f2b6e.webm?t=1727516037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fully Destructible Terrain!</h2>Many weapons can cause explosions that destroy parts of the terrain. With a good aim, you can eliminate an enemy by strategically destroying the ground under them, sending them to the water below!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/ad9ad33c77c0a5297fe8b0290a6cb39e.avif?t=1727516037\" width=530 height=120 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Disasters can be surprisingly deadly!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/2168b0a3a0dfe44c3c7b9cf97688e87f.poster.avif?t=1727516037\" width=600 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/2168b0a3a0dfe44c3c7b9cf97688e87f.webm?t=1727516037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754920/extras/2168b0a3a0dfe44c3c7b9cf97688e87f.mp4?t=1727516037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
